---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="(주)성산연구소 (DEEPSOUND) | 휴대용 PAUT 검사장비, 스캐너 시스템 및 소프트웨어"
	description="(주)성산연구소(DEEPSOUND)의 초음파 비파괴검사(NDT) 정밀 하드웨어 및 전용 소프트웨어(DSVision/DSViewer) 솔루션. 글로벌 표준 PAUT 장비와 소프트웨어를 소개합니다."
	lang="ko"
>
	<!-- Hero Section with Deep Navy Dark Theme and Neon Cyan Glows -->
	<section class="relative bg-[#0C1929] text-white overflow-hidden py-24 sm:py-32 border-b border-slate-800">
		<!-- Glowing Background Accents -->
		<div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-96 h-96 bg-primary-cyan/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
		<div class="absolute bottom-10 right-1/4 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-blue-600/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
		
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-8 items-center">
				
				<!-- Hero Left Content -->
				<div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-8">
					<div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-xs text-primary-cyan font-semibold tracking-wide">
						<span>초음파 비파괴검사 전문 브랜드: DEEPSOUND</span>
					</div>
					
					<h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight font-display leading-tight">
						정밀 PAUT 하드웨어와 <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-cyan to-blue-400">실시간 계측·분석 소프트웨어</span>
					</h1>
					
					<p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
						(주)성산연구소가 직접 연구·개발해 온 DEEPSOUND는 휴대용 PAUT 장비부터 다채널 랙마운트 시스템, 전용 데이터 획득(Acquisition) 및 분석 소프트웨어까지 현장 기술자들을 위한 통합 비파괴검사 솔루션을 제공합니다.
					</p>
					
					<!-- Simulated Pagefind Document Search Bar -->
					<div class="max-w-lg">
						<form class="relative group" action="/ko/resources/">
							<div class="absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-cyan to-blue-500 rounded-lg blur opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-60 transition duration-300"></div>
							<div class="relative bg-slate-950/90 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg flex items-center p-1.5 pl-4">
								<svg class="h-5 w-5 text-slate-400 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" />
								</svg>
								<input 
									type="text" 
									name="q"
									placeholder="장비 매뉴얼, 데이터시트, 인증서 또는 소프트웨어 설치파일 검색..." 
									class="bg-transparent text-sm text-white placeholder-slate-500 w-full focus:outline-none pr-4"
								/>
								<button type="submit" class="bg-primary-cyan text-slate-950 text-xs font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-cyan-400 transition-all flex-shrink-0">
									자료 검색
								</button>
							</div>
						</form>
						<p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-2 ml-1">
							추천 검색어: <span class="text-primary-cyan/80">P5 매뉴얼</span>, <span class="text-primary-cyan/80">DSVision 업데이트</span>, <span class="text-primary-cyan/80">시험 인증서</span>
						</p>
					</div>
					
					<!-- Primary Action Buttons -->
					<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-2">
						<a href="#products" class="px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-bold text-slate-950 bg-primary-cyan hover:bg-[#00cbe6] rounded-md shadow-lg transition-all duration-200">
							제품 라인업 보기
						</a>
						<a href="/ko/resources/" class="px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-bold text-white border border-slate-700 hover:border-slate-500 rounded-md hover:bg-slate-900 transition-all duration-200">
							기술 자료실 바로가기
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<!-- Hero Right Visual -->
				<div class="lg:col-span-5 relative flex justify-center items-center">
					<div class="absolute w-80 h-80 bg-primary-cyan/15 rounded-full blur-2xl"></div>
					
					<div class="relative w-full max-w-md aspect-square bg-slate-950/40 border border-slate-800/80 rounded-2xl p-8 backdrop-blur-md shadow-2xl flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden">
						<div class="absolute -right-16 -bottom-16 w-64 h-64 rounded-full border border-primary-cyan/20 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none">
							<div class="w-48 h-48 rounded-full border border-primary-cyan/10 flex items-center justify-center">
								<div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full border border-primary-cyan/5"></div>
							</div>
						</div>
						
						<!-- Simulated Hardware Card -->
						<div class="relative bg-slate-900/90 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-xl p-4 shadow-lg transform -rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-300 space-y-3 z-10">
							<div class="flex justify-between items-center">
								<span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-primary-cyan uppercase tracking-wider">NDT 장비 사양</span>
								<span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-0.5 bg-slate-800 text-slate-400 rounded-full font-mono">12.1" LCD</span>
							</div>
							<h3 class="text-base font-bold text-white">DEEPSOUND P5</h3>
							<p class="text-xs text-slate-400 leading-snug">수많은 PAUT 기술자들의 피드백을 반영하여 험난한 산업 현장에서도 극도의 편의성과 빠른 조작 속도를 보장합니다.</p>
							<div class="flex gap-2">
								<span class="text-[10px] bg-slate-800 text-slate-300 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">PAUT</span>
								<span class="text-[10px] bg-slate-800 text-slate-300 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">TOFD</span>
								<span class="text-[10px] bg-slate-800 text-slate-300 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">멀티그룹</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						
						<!-- Simulated Software Card -->
						<div class="relative bg-slate-900/90 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-xl p-4 shadow-lg transform translate-x-8 -translate-y-4 rotate-3 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-300 space-y-3 z-20">
							<div class="flex justify-between items-center">
								<span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-[#3B82F6] uppercase tracking-wider">Acquisition 소프트웨어</span>
								<span class="text-[10px] text-green-400 flex items-center space-x-1">
									<span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-green-400 rounded-full animate-ping"></span>
									<span>실시간 측정 중</span>
								</span>
							</div>
							<h3 class="text-base font-bold text-white">DSVision</h3>
							<div class="h-16 w-full bg-slate-950 rounded border border-slate-800 flex items-center justify-between px-3 overflow-hidden font-mono text-[9px] text-primary-cyan/80">
								<div class="space-y-1">
									<div>두께 측정: 24.5mm</div>
									<div>진폭 감도: 88% FSH</div>
								</div>
								<div class="flex items-end space-x-0.5 h-10 w-24">
									<div class="bg-[#3B82F6]/40 w-2 h-3"></div>
									<div class="bg-[#3B82F6]/60 w-2 h-6"></div>
									<div class="bg-primary-cyan w-2 h-9"></div>
									<div class="bg-[#3B82F6]/60 w-2 h-4"></div>
									<div class="bg-[#3B82F6]/40 w-2 h-2"></div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Trust Bar -->
	<section class="bg-slate-900 border-b border-slate-800 py-6 text-slate-400">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
				<div class="pt-4 sm:pt-0">
					<p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">독자 기술력</p>
					<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 mt-1">H/W 및 S/W 자체 연구개발</p>
				</div>
				<div class="pt-4 sm:pt-0">
					<p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">고정밀 검사</p>
					<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 mt-1">PAUT 및 TOFD 멀티 채널 지원</p>
				</div>
				<div class="pt-4 sm:pt-0">
					<p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">신속한 지원</p>
					<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 mt-1">고객 맞춤 SDK 제공 및 사후 관리</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- B2B Quick Navigation Links -->
	<section class="py-12 bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4">
				{[
					{ title: "정밀 장비 사양", desc: "모델별 스펙 비교", href: "/ko/products/" },
					{ title: "NDT 소프트웨어", desc: "실시간 계측 및 분석", href: "/ko/software/" },
					{ title: "장비 매뉴얼", desc: "사용법 가이드북", href: "/ko/resources/" },
					{ title: "제품 카탈로그", desc: "최신 공식 브로슈어", href: "/ko/resources/" },
					{ title: "품질 인증서", desc: "인증 파일 일괄 획득", href: "/ko/resources/" }
				].map((item) => (
					<a href={item.href} class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-primary-cyan hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
						<h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">{item.title}</h3>
						<p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">{item.desc}</p>
					</a>
				))}
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Featured NDT Products -->
	<section id="products" class="py-24 bg-white scroll-mt-16">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight font-display">
					DEEPSOUND 정밀 비파괴 검사(NDT) 하드웨어
				</h2>
				<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
					휴대용 정밀 PAUT/UT 장비부터 자동화 설비(OEM) 연동을 위한 대채널 랙마운트 시스템 보드까지 고신뢰도의 NDT 하드웨어 솔루션을 제공합니다.
				</p>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Part 1: Portable NDT Instruments -->
			<div class="mt-16 border-b border-slate-100 pb-4">
				<div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
					<span class="px-2.5 py-0.5 bg-slate-900 text-primary-cyan text-xs font-mono font-bold rounded">CATEGORY 01</span>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">휴대용 PAUT & 초음파 탐상 장비 (Portable Instruments)</h3>
				</div>
				<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">다양한 현장 환경에서 단독 휴대 및 편리한 조작을 극대화한 초경량·고신뢰성 모델 라인업입니다.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-8">
				<!-- P5 Card -->
				<div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:border-slate-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between">
					<div class="p-6 space-y-4">
						<div class="flex justify-between items-start">
							<div>
								<span class="text-xs font-bold text-primary-cyan bg-slate-900 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wider">프리미엄 모델</span>
								<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-2">DEEPSOUND P5</h3>
							</div>
						</div>
						<p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
							12.1인치 고해상도 대화면과 신속한 부팅 및 초고속 작동 속도를 갖추어 뛰어난 조작성을 보장합니다. 가혹한 산업 현장에서도 신속하고 정확하게 결함을 검출합니다.
						</p>
						
						<!-- Specs Badge Grid -->
						<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 pt-2">
							<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-2 text-center text-xs">
								<span class="block text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase font-mono">화면 사양</span>
								<span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">12.1" LCD</span>
							</div>
							<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-2 text-center text-xs">
								<span class="block text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase font-mono">하드웨어 채널</span>
								<span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">32/128PR</span>
							</div>
							<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-2 text-center text-xs">
								<span class="block text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase font-mono">검사 기법</span>
								<span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">PAUT + TOFD</span>
							</div>
							<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-2 text-center text-xs">
								<span class="block text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase font-mono">전용 프로그램</span>
								<span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">DSVision 내장</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="p-6 bg-slate-100 border-t border-slate-200 flex justify-between items-center gap-4">
						<a href="/ko/resources/" class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900">카탈로그 받기</a>
						<a href="/ko/products/" class="px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold text-slate-900 bg-primary-cyan rounded hover:bg-cyan-400 transition-colors">상세보기</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- B3 Card -->
				<div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:border-slate-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between">
					<div class="p-6 space-y-4">
						<div class="flex justify-between items-start">
							<div>
								<span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 bg-slate-200 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wider">최상의 가성비</span>
								<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-2">DEEPSOUND B3</h3>
							</div>
						</div>
						<p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
							배터리를 포함하고도 2kg 미만의 경량 설계를 실현하여 뛰어난 휴대성을 자랑합니다. 컴팩트한 바디에 높은 경제성을 갖추었으며, 프리미엄 P5 모델과 완전히 호환되는 실시간 수집 엔진을 제공합니다.
						</p>
						
						<!-- Specs Badge Grid -->
						<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 pt-2">
							<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-2 text-center text-xs">
								<span class="block text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase font-mono">장비 무게</span>
								<span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">&lt; 2.0kg (배터리 포함)</span>
							</div>
							<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-2 text-center text-xs">
								<span class="block text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase font-mono">소프트웨어</span>
								<span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">P5와 100% 호환</span>
							</div>
							<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-2 text-center text-xs">
								<span class="block text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase font-mono">편의성</span>
								<span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">컴팩트 설계</span>
							</div>
							<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-2 text-center text-xs">
								<span class="block text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase font-mono">투자 효율</span>
								<span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">가성비 최우수</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="p-6 bg-slate-100 border-t border-slate-200 flex justify-between items-center gap-4">
						<a href="/ko/resources/" class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900">데이터시트 받기</a>
						<a href="/ko/products/" class="px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold text-slate-900 bg-primary-cyan rounded hover:bg-cyan-400 transition-colors">상세보기</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- T3 Card -->
				<div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:border-slate-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between">
					<div class="p-6 space-y-4">
						<div class="flex justify-between items-start">
							<div>
								<span class="text-xs font-bold text-blue-600 bg-blue-100 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wider">초경량 차세대</span>
								<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-2">DEEPSOUND T3</h3>
							</div>
						</div>
						<p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
							0.9kg 초경량 무게와 7인치 고선명 터치 스크린을 결합하여 극대화된 현장 기동성을 자랑합니다. 한 손 조작이 가능하며 TOFD 전용 솔루션을 기본 탑재하여 협소한 현장에서도 완벽한 검사가 가능합니다.
						</p>
						
						<!-- Specs Badge Grid -->
						<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 pt-2">
							<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-2 text-center text-xs">
								<span class="block text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase font-mono">장비 무게</span>
								<span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">0.9kg (초경량)</span>
							</div>
							<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-2 text-center text-xs">
								<span class="block text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase font-mono">화면 크기</span>
								<span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">7.0" 터치 LCD</span>
							</div>
							<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-2 text-center text-xs">
								<span class="block text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase font-mono">검사 기법</span>
								<span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">TOFD 기본 탑재</span>
							</div>
							<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-2 text-center text-xs">
								<span class="block text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase font-mono">기동성</span>
								<span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">한 손 조작 가능</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="p-6 bg-slate-100 border-t border-slate-200 flex justify-between items-center gap-4">
						<a href="/ko/resources/" class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900">브로슈어 받기</a>
						<a href="/ko/products/" class="px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold text-slate-900 bg-primary-cyan rounded hover:bg-cyan-400 transition-colors">상세보기</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Part 2: Automated & OEM System Boards -->
			<div class="mt-20 border-b border-slate-100 pb-4">
				<div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
